snippet: Wanas, a rural estate and arts foundation, celebrates 25 years of installations by artists including Yoko Ono, Marina Abramovic and Roxy Paine.
abstract: Wanas, a rural estate and arts foundation in Ostra Goinge, Sweden, celebrates 25 years of installations by artists; park has more than 50 permanent outdoor artworks, plus large-scale installations and temporary exhibitions in former farm buildings; unusual arts destination attracts nearly 80,000 visitors each year.
lead_paragraph: Wanas, a rural estate and arts foundation, celebrates 25 years of installations by artists including Yoko Ono, Marina Abramovic and Roxy Paine.

headline.seo: In a Swedish Park, Art Co-Stars With Nature
headline.main: In a Swedish Park, Art Co-Stars With Nature
